lass=\"card heroCard\"><div class=\"img\"><span class=\"place\">📍 Москва</span></div><div class=\"body\"><div class=\"kicker\"><h3 class=\"title\">История и гастрономия</h3><span class=\"status\">Ждёт гида</span></div><p class=\"subtitle\">Небольшая группа хочет увидеть город без стандартного маршрута.</p><div class=\"seats\"><span class=\"avatar\"></span><span class=\"avatar\"></span><span class=\"avatar\"></span><span class=\"avatar\"></span><span class=\"mini\">4 joined · 1 seat needed</span></div><div class=\"progress\"><i></i></div><div class=\"facts\"><div class=\"fact\"><span class=\"dot\">30</span>30 июня · гибкие даты</div><div class=\"fact\"><span class=\"dot\">₽</span>4 000 ₽ / человек</div></div><div class=\"btn\">Присоединиться</div></div></article><article class=\"card heroCard\"><div class=\"img\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0e3658,#8bb5d8)\"><span class=\"place\">📍 Казань</span></div><div class=\"body\"><div class=\"kicker\"><h3 class=\"title\">Кухня и старый город</h3><span class=\"status\">2 места</span></div><p class=\"subtitle\">Пара путешественников ищет местного гида на спокойную прогулку.</p><div class=\"seats\"><span class=\"avatar\"></span><span class=\"avatar\"></span><span class=\"mini\">2 joined · group forming</span></div><div class=\"progress\"><i style=\"width:45%\"></i></div><div class=\"facts\"><div class=\"fact\"><span class=\"dot\">1</span>1–2 октября · 11:00–16:00</div><div class=\"fact\"><span class=\"dot\">₽</span>2 600 ₽ / человек</div></div><div class=\"btn\">Присоединиться</div></div></article></div></div></section>\n./docs/qa/finish-website-2026-06-28/requests-card-redesign-proposals.html:26:  <section class=\"section\"><h2>2. Compact Decision Card</h2><p>Less pretty, more functional. Good when there are many requests.</p><div class=\"compare\"><div class=\"notes\"><b>Why it is better:</b><ul><li>Cards become scannable like a premium marketplace.</li><li>Image supports, but does not dominate.</li><li>Perfect for desktop list and mobile saved items.</li></ul></div><div class=\"grid2\"><article class=\"card compact\"><div class=\"img\"><span class=\"place\">Москва</span></div><div class=\"body\"><div class=\"kicker\"><h3 class=\"title\">5 travelers · 30 June</h3><span class=\"status\">Ждёт гида</span></div><p class=\"subtitle\">История, культура, гастрономия · flexible dates</p><div class=\"facts\"><div class=\"fact\"><span class=\"dot\">👥</span>Group is almost ready</div><div class=\"fact\"><span class=\"dot\">₽</span>4 000 ₽ / person</div></div><div class=\"pricebar\"><div class=\"mini\">Need a guide response</div><div class=\"btn\">Join</div></div></div></article><article class=\"card compact\"><div class=\"img\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0c2136,#6e9fc8)\"><span class=\"place\">Элиста</span></div><div class=\"body\"><div class=\"kicker\"><h3 class=\"title\">10 travelers · today</h3><span class=\"status\">Скоро</span></div><p class=\"subtitle\">Nature, food, local culture · 11:00–13:00</p><div class=\"facts\"><div class=\"fact\"><span class=\"dot\">👥</span>Large group, high demand</div><div class=\"fact\"><span class=\"dot\">₽</span>2 000 ₽ / person</div></div><div class=\"pricebar\"><div class=\"mini\">Best for local guides</div><div class=\"btn\">Join</div></div></div></article></div></div></section>\n./docs/qa/finish-website-2026-06-28/requests-card-redesign-proposals.html:28:  <section class=\"section\"><h2>3. Guide‑First Offer Card</h2><p>For guides, the card should answer: is this worth my time?</p><div class=\"compare\"><div class=\"notes\"><b>Guide questions answered:</b><ul><li>How many travelers?</li><li>When?</li><li>Budget?</li><li>What kind of tour?</li><li>Can I send an offer now?</li></ul></div><article class=\"card guideCard\"><div class=\"body\"><div class=\"kicker\"><h3 class=\"title\">Москва · 5 travelers waiting</h3><span class=\"status\">Open request</span></div><p class=\"subtitle\">They want history, culture, and food. Flexible date, 11:00–13:00. Good fit for a 2-hour private route.</p><div class=\"chips\"><span class=\"chip\">История</span><span class=\"chip\">Гастрономия</span><span class=\"chip\">Flexible date</span><span class=\"chip\">Group request</span></div><div class=\"facts\"><div class=\"fact\"><span class=\"dot\">✓</span>Traveler intent is clear enough to price</div><div class=\"fact\"><span class=\"dot\">!</span>No guide has answered yet</div></div></div><div class=\"right\"><div><div class=\"metric\"><b>4 000 ₽</b><span>per traveler</span></div><div class=\"metric\"><b>5 people</b><span>group size</span></div><div class=\"metric\"><b>30 June</b><span>date</span></div></div><div class=\"btn\">Предложить тур</div></div></article></div></section>\n./docs/qa/finish-website-2026-06-28/requests-card-redesign-proposals.html:30:  <section class=\"section\"><h2>4. Before → After card hierarchy</h2><p>Same content, but the new card removes visual noise and makes the decision path obvious.</p><div class=\"beforeafter\"><article class=\"card old\"><div class=\"label\">current style problem</div><div class=\"img\"><span class=\"place\">Россия</span></div><div class=\"body\"><div class=\"kicker\"><h3 class=\"title\">Москва</h3><span class=\"status\">Ждёт гида</span></div><div class=\"chips\"><span class=\"chip\">Сборная группа</span><span class=\"chip\">от 5 чел.</span></div><div class=\"facts\"><div class=\"fact\">30 июня · Гибкие даты</div><div class=\"fact\">11:00–13:00</div><div class=\"fact\">История и культура · Гастрономия</div></div><div class=\"pricebar\"><div class=\"price\"><b>4 000 ₽</b><span>/ чел</span></div></div><div class=\"btn\">Присоединиться</div></div></article><article class=\"card decision\"><div class=\"label\">proposed simpler hierarchy</div><div class=\"body\"><div class=\"kicker\"><h3 class=\"title\">5 people want a Moscow tour</h3><span class=\"status\">No guide yet</span></div><p class=\"subtitle\">History + food · 30 June · 11:00–13:00</p><div class=\"seats\"><span class=\"avatar\"></span><span class=\"avatar\"></span><span class=\"avatar\"></span><span class=\"avatar\"></span><span class=\"mini\">Group almost formed</span></div><div class=\"progress\"><i style=\"width:82%\"></i></div><div class=\"pricebar\"><div class=\"price\"><b>4 000 ₽</b><span>per person</span></div><div class=\"btn\">Join group</div></div></div></article></div></section>\n./docs/qa/finish-website-2026-06-28/requests-card-redesign-proposals.html:32:  <section class=\"section\"><h2>5. Mobile card</h2><p>Mobile should not be a squeezed desktop card. It should be one clean decision per screen.</p><div class=\"grid3\"><article class=\"card mobile\"><div class=\"img\"><span class=\"place\">Москва</span></div><div class=\"body\"><h3 class=\"title\">Join 5 travelers in Moscow</h3><p class=\"subtitle\">30 June · History + food · 4 000 ₽</p><div class=\"seats\"><span class=\"avatar\"></span><span class=\"avatar\"></span><span class=\"avatar\"></span><span class=\"mini\">Almost ready</span></div><div class=\"btn\">Присоединиться</div></div></article><article class=\"card mobile\"><div class=\"body\"><h3 class=\"title\">Москва</h3><p class=\"subtitle\">5 travelers need a local guide for history and food.</p><div class=\"facts\"><div class=\"fact\"><span class=\"dot\">📅</span>30 июня · 11:00–13:00</div><div class=\"fact\"><span class=\"dot\">👥</span>Group request · almost full</div><div class=\"fact\"><span class=\"dot\">₽</span>4 000 ₽ / человек</div></div><div class=\"btn\">Присоединиться</div></div></article><article class=\"card mobile\"><div class=\"body\"><span class=\"status\">Recommended</span><h3 class=\"title\" style=\"margin-top:12px\">A guide can answer this today</h3><p class=\"subtitle\">Show one “best next step” instead of many equal details.</p><div class=\"btn\">View request</div><div class=\"btn secondary\" style=\"margin-top:8px\">Save</div></div></article></div></section>\n./docs/audits/theme-vocabularies-and-guide-specializations.md:81:- Grep 