: \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"docs/qa/page-refactor-audit-2026-06-28/public-_auth_forgot-password-375.png\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\n./docs/qa/page-refactor-audit-2026-06-28/summary.json:157:      \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"redirected to auth\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\n./docs/qa/page-refactor-audit-2026-06-28/summary.json:406:    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"h1\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Политика конфиденциальности Provodnik\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\n./docs/qa/page-refactor-audit-2026-06-28/summary.json:421:    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"h1\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Политика конфиденциальности Provodnik\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\n./docs/qa/page-refactor-audit-2026-06-28/summary.json:436:    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"h1\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Пользовательское соглашение Provodnik\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\n./docs/qa/page-refactor-audit-2026-06-28/summary.json:451:    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"h1\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Пользовательское соглашение Provodnik\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\n./docs/business/investor/provodnik-investor-ru.html:6:    <title>Provodnik Investor RU</title>\\\\\\\\n./docs/business/investor/provodnik-investor-ru.html:404:            <div class=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"hero-copy\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\">Provodnik — мобильный маркетплейс экскурсий и туров по России, который закрывает ту часть рынка, где спрос и предложение до сих пор плохо оцифрованы: Telegram-чаты, звонки, личные договоренности, ручной сбор групп и дорогие агрегаторы с высоким take rate.</div>\\\\\\\\n./docs/business/investor/provodnik-investor-ru.html:411:<div class=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"proof-item\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"><strong>24%+ vs 10-15%</strong><span>Публичная комиссия Sputnik8 — 24% и выше. Целевой take rate Provodnik — 10–15%.</span></div>\\\\\\\\n./docs/business/investor/provodnik-investor-ru.html:426:            <div class=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"body\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"><strong>1. Спрос подтвержден рынком.</strong> Крупные игроки уже доказали наличие спроса, доверительных механизмов и готовности пользователей платить за бронирование экскурсий онлайн.<br /><br /><strong>2. У incumbents есть слабое место.</strong> Они сильны в listing-first логике, но заметно слабее в custom demand, бюджетных сценариях и user-led group formation.<br /><br /><strong>3. Wedge Provodnik понятен.</strong> Пользователь создает запрос по датам, бюджету и формату, другие путешественники могут присоединиться, а гиды отвечают структурированными офферами.<br /><br /><strong>4. GTM дисциплинированный.</strong> Запуск с 1–3 регионов и низкорисковых категорий позволяет сначала доказать ликвидность, а не размывать операционную фокусировку.</div>\\\\\\\\n./docs/business/investor/provodnik-investor-ru.html:442:          <div class=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"footer-mark\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\">Provodnik · Investor RU PDF</div>\\\\\\\\n./docs/business/investor/provodnik-investor-ru.html:504:          <div class=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"footer-mark\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\">Provodnik · Investor RU PDF</div>\\\\\\\\n./docs/business/investor/provodnik-investor-one-pager.json:3:    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Provodnik Investor One-Pager\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\n./docs/business/investor/provodnik-investor-one-pager.json:7:    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"hero_copy\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Provodnik is built for the part of the category incumbents do not organize well enough: <strong>custom traveler demand</strong>, <strong>budget-led group formation</strong>, and <strong>regional supply still selling through manual channels</strong>. The model combines listings with request-driven booking, structured guide offers, trust controls, and a target commission of <strong>10% to 15%</strong>.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\n./docs/business/investor/provodnik-investor-one-pager.json:20:      \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"copy\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Sputnik8 public commission versus Provodnik target take rate.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\n./docs/business/investor/provodnik-investor-one-pager.json:42:    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"body\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"<strong>Problem:</strong> travelers struggle to find the right excursion for budget, dates, format, and trust; guides rely on expensive aggregators or fragmented offline channels.<br /><br /><strong>Wedge:</strong> Provodnik is not another catalog. It is a <strong>request-first marketplace</strong> where travelers can create demand, join others into groups, and receive structured offers from verified guides.<br /><br /><strong>Why this can win:</strong> lower commission matters only when paired with new demand capture. Provodnik competes on liquidity for <strong>custom and budget-sensitive demand</strong>, not on listing breadth alone.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\n./docs/business/investor/provodnik-investor-one-pager.json:63:    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Provodnik targets the less organized motion: traveler requests, budget-led group economics, and local guide supply outside polished catalog systems.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\n./docs/business/investor/provodnik-investor-one-pager.json:88:  \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"footer_mark\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Provodnik · Executive Investor Summary\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\n./docs/qa/finish-website-2026-06-28/discovery-sections-forensics/metrics.json:9:    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Запросы — Provodnik\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\n./docs/qa/finish-website-2026-06-28/discovery-sections-forensics/metrics.json:54:    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Запросы — Provodnik\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\n./docs/qa/finish-website-2026-06-28/discovery-sections-forensics/metrics.json:99:    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Экскурсии — Provodnik\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\n./docs/qa/finish-website-2026-06-28/discovery-sections-forensics/metrics.json:195:    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Экскурсии — Provodnik\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\n./docs/qa/finish-website-2026-06-28/discovery-sections-forensics/metrics.json:291:    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Гиды — Provodnik\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\n./docs/